    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Crumble</strong> the stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> into the pork mince with the smoked paprika, garlic and dill&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cook</strong> for 1-2 min</p>\r\n<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, add the Dijon to a measuring jug with 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> boiling water</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
