      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> flour to the pan and stir thoroughly</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the Dijon/water mixture to the pan and continue to stir - this will create a sauce</p>",
